message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this excellent product. Given its value, I'm asking for $11,000. What do you think?
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I can only pay up to $9,000. Looking forward to your response.
Hi Bob, I understand your position, but $9,000 is a bit too low for me. Could you consider $10,500? This would be a fair compromise.
Thank you for adjusting your offer, Alice. I can't go above $9,500 for the product. Let me know if this works for you.
